---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Mobile Offload | Goolsby Ventures LLC"
  description="Privacy Policy for Mobile Offload, operated by Goolsby Ventures LLC. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties."
>
  <Nav />
  <main id="main">
    <section class="relative py-24" style="background: var(--color-bg-base);">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"
           style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 50% 0%, rgba(27,111,235,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase"
               style="background: var(--color-primary-muted); color: var(--color-accent); font-family: var(--font-body); border: 1px solid rgba(27,111,235,0.2);">
            Legal
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="text-base" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-family: var(--font-body);">
            Effective Date: April 8, 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Last Updated: April 8, 2026
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-xl" style="background: var(--color-bg-surface); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.25);">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-success); font-family: var(--font-body);">
              We do not sell, rent, share, or trade your personal information — ever.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="prose-custom">

          <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            Mobile Offload is a service operated by <strong>Goolsby Ventures LLC</strong>, a California limited liability company
            located at 19277 Sellens View Court, Redding, California 96003. Goolsby Ventures LLC is the primary business entity
            responsible for all operations, data handling, and contractual relationships associated with the Mobile Offload platform.
          </p>
          <p>
            Mobile Offload operates in partnership with <strong>Hudson House</strong>, which serves as a brokerage partner in
            facilitating carrier offload network agreements. Hudson House does not independently collect, store, or process
            end-user personal data submitted through this website.
          </p>

          <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you submit a qualification form or contact us, we may collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your name and business name</li>
            <li>Email address and phone number</li>
            <li>Business address and venue type</li>
            <li>Estimated daily foot traffic</li>
            <li>Any additional details you voluntarily provide in the message field</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We also collect standard web analytics data (page views, browser type, referring URL) through privacy-respecting
            tools. This data is aggregated and never tied to an individual identity.
          </p>

          <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>Information you provide is used solely to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Evaluate whether your location qualifies for the Mobile Offload carrier network program</li>
            <li>Contact you about your inquiry and next steps</li>
            <li>Send program updates if you have opted in</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We will never use your information for unrelated marketing, and we will never sell or transfer it to data brokers,
            advertisers, or third-party marketers.
          </p>

          <h2>4. We Do Not Share Your Data</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Goolsby Ventures LLC does not sell, rent, lease, or share your personal information with any third party</strong>,
            except in the following limited circumstances:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Hudson House (Brokerage Partner):</strong> As our brokerage partner, Hudson House may receive the minimum
              information necessary to facilitate a carrier agreement on your behalf. This is disclosed to you prior to any
              such sharing and is subject to the same confidentiality standards.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Carrier Partners (AT&T, T-Mobile, Google Fi):</strong> If you proceed with a deployment agreement,
              only the business-level information required for the carrier contract (business name, address, point of contact)
              is shared — never personal financial or consumer data.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> We may disclose information if required to do so by law or in response to
              a valid legal process (e.g., court order or subpoena).
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take the security of your information seriously. All data transmitted through this website is encrypted via
            TLS/HTTPS. Form submissions are processed through Web3Forms, a secure third-party form service that does not
            store your data beyond delivery to our inbox. We do not maintain an internal database of form submissions
            beyond our own email records.
          </p>
          <p>
            The carrier offload network infrastructure itself operates with full WPA3 enterprise-grade encryption and
            complete network separation between carrier traffic and your existing business network.
          </p>

          <h2>6. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
          <p>
            This website uses minimal, privacy-respecting analytics only. We do not use advertising cookies, tracking pixels,
            or fingerprinting technologies. We do not participate in cross-site behavioral tracking.
          </p>

          <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Request a copy of any personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your information from our records</li>
            <li>Opt out of any future communications at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@mobileoffload.com">support@mobileoffload.com</a>.
            We will respond within 10 business days.
          </p>

          <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            This website is intended for business owners and operators and is not directed at individuals under the age of 18.
            We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.
          </p>

          <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated
            effective date. Continued use of the website following any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.
          </p>

          <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us:</p>
          <div class="contact-block">
            <p><strong>Goolsby Ventures LLC</strong><br/>
            Operating as: Mobile Offload<br/>
            19277 Sellens View Court<br/>
            Redding, California 96003</p>
            <p>
              Phone: <a href="tel:+15302768183">(530) 276-8183</a><br/>
              Email: <a href="mailto:support@mobileoffload.com">support@mobileoffload.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>Brokerage Partner: Hudson House</p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Back link -->
        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-200"
             style="color: var(--color-accent); font-family: var(--font-body);"
             onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--color-text-primary)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--color-accent)'">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/>
            </svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  .prose-custom {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .prose-custom h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .prose-custom p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-custom ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-custom ul li {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .prose-custom ul li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .prose-custom strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .prose-custom a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .prose-custom a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  .prose-custom .contact-block {
    background: var(--color-bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .prose-custom .contact-block p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-custom .contact-block p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
